{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2541012, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 485303, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "虽然dz略暴躁，不过确实认为公用洗衣机不该用来洗内衣裤", "timestamp": 1631982443, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2541016, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 485303, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "容易交叉感染", "timestamp": 1631982482, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2541023, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 485303, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "说的太好了", "timestamp": 1631982508, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2541041, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 485303, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "《知识分子》的恐怖之处就在于懒居然都能懒得有法可依，牛！", "timestamp": 1631982645, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2541098, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 485303, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "虽然我在家里也用洗衣机洗袜子，但学校里公共洗衣机的话袜子内裤还是手洗。因为懒而不考虑他人感受真是这里的一大特色。", "timestamp": 1631982932, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2541139, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 485303, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "sb，你算老几？", "timestamp": 1631983148, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2541160, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 485303, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我用消毒液", "timestamp": 1631983276, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2541161, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 485303, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "但还是抱歉", "timestamp": 1631983285, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2541189, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 485303, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我在家被妈宠着不洗 回学校自己洗不干净的大件可以送干洗店", "timestamp": 1631983426, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2541196, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 485303, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "没有办法解决 有人要用洗衣机洗内衣内裤和鞋子 我就只能不用洗衣机里", "timestamp": 1631983477, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2543265, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 485303, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "首先，懒不懒是道德要求，是用来要求自己的。\n其次，“懒得有法可依”背后的逻辑是，法律是对人最低的道德要求，这一点毛病都没有。\n最后，你有不使用洗衣机的权利，但是没有剥夺他人使用的权利，这是他人通过付费向洗衣机运营方取得的合法权利，和你没有关系。", "timestamp": 1632023307, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2547469, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 485303, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "你寄吧谁啊？哈哈", "timestamp": 1632062583, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2553623, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 485303, "reply_to": 2543265, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 谁寄吧剥夺你使用洗衣机的权力了？只是单纯的骂你啊，自己对号入座关我什么事？", "timestamp": 1632129728, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 5, "pid": 485303, "reply": 13, "tag": "引战", "text": "各位懒人来冲，坚决反对洗衣机洗袜子/鞋子/内裤，你内裤上沾着屎自己脱下来看看，dz坚持手洗内衣裤，边洗澡就洗了很方便，这么大了手洗衣服都干不了，还理直气壮觉得天经地义，你以后自己过爱怎么洗怎么洗谁都管不着，那些收集一团内裤袜子一起搅的这辈子就这么过吧，开心第一！！！或者建议把光辉事迹给你母亲汇报一下？从小娇生惯养的东西，自己娘洗了衣服也从来没考虑过辛苦吧！", "timestamp": 1631982374, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1632129728, "url": "", "vote": {}}}